(90, 1, '2021-05-29 02:39:17', '2021-05-29 02:39:17', 'Strawberry Milk Tea is one of the best sellers in our milkshake line. Please visit our shop to know more about our product. Also, follow us on Facebook and Twitter.', 'Strawberry Milk Tea', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'strawberry-milk-tea', '', '', '2021-05-29 02:39:22', '2021-05-29 02:39:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sabino_kap/?post_type=product&#038;p=90', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2021-05-29 02:41:47', '2021-05-29 02:41:47', 'Okinawa Milk Tea or Roasted Milk Tea uses a special roasted brown sugar. ... Apart from using the brown sugar syrup to line the glass as \"tiger stripes\" it\'s also traditionally made with tapioca balls that are sauteed in brown sugar\r\n\r\nThe Okinawa is essentially milk tea made with roasted brown sugar instead of regular syrup, giving it a distinct flavor and adding a layer of complexity to the traditional drink.', 'Okinawa Milk Tea', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '91', '', '', '2021-05-29 02:42:16', '2021-05-29 02:42:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sabino_kap/?post_type=product&#038;p=91', 0, 'product', '', 0),
