(93, 1, '2021-05-29 02:48:00', '2021-05-29 02:48:00', 'The slight sweetness from fresh honeydew and it\'s unique melon flavor make milktea tea such a delicious and refreshing beverage. ... Honeydew milk tea is popular for those that like lightly sweet milk tea.', 'Honeydew Milk Tea', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'honeydew-milk-tea', '', '', '2021-05-29 02:48:04', '2021-05-29 02:48:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sabino_kap/?post_type=product&#038;p=93', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2021-05-29 02:49:56', '2021-05-29 02:49:56', 'Hokkaido milk tea is made of black tea leaves with milk — traditionally from fresh milk produced in the Hokkaido province. The tea is made using high-quality black tea leaves including Assam, Darjeeling, and Earl Grey varieties. The tea is often sweetened with caramel syrup or brown sugar.', 'Hokaiddo Milk Tea', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hokaiddo-milk-tea', '', '', '2021-05-29 02:50:00', '2021-05-29 02:50:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sabino_kap/?post_type=product&#038;p=94', 0, 'product', '', 0),
